net.jawr.web.resource.bundle.generator.resolver

Interface ResourceGeneratorResolver

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    PrefixedPathResolver, ResourceGeneratorResolverWrapper, SuffixedPathResolver

    public interface ResourceGeneratorResolver
    This interface defines the matcher which will be used to determine if the ResourceGenerator is responsible to handle a path
